At The Park Hotel, Kolkata, your day begins with elegance — plush rooms, curated spaces, and the signature charm of a true luxury escape. 🌿

But the real magic unfolds after midnight.
From 12 AM to 4 AM, indulge in the city’s most exclusive late-night continental experience — served fresh, flavorful, and with a 30% discount. 🍷🥐
A rare offering in Kolkata — where luxury doesn’t sleep, and taste never compromises.

Whether it’s a day to unwind or a night to remember — this is where Kolkata’s finest moments happen.
